title: Indonesia GDP Deflator
description: GDP Deflator in Indonesia increased to 171.03 points in the third quarter of 2022 from 168.28 points in the second quarter of 2022. GDP Deflator in Indonesia averaged 145.08 points from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 264.61 points in the fourth quarter of 2009 and a record low of 95.07 points in the first quarter of 2000. This page provides - Indonesia GDP Deflator - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Indonesia
